# PS5 Demo Copy Guardrails

## Allowed player-facing phrases
- Eligible replacement option
- Included replacement
- Upgrade options available
- Recommended option
- Confirm replacement
- Confirm delivery details
- Demo checkout
- Confirmation
- Estimated delivery
- Tracking preview
- Email confirmation preview
- We'll continue monitoring
- You're eligible for...
- Based on your controller status and PlayStation activity...

## Banned player-facing phrases
Never use these in any component, journey data, or UI string:

- support review requested
- pending support review
- our team will review
- case created / case routed
- claim created
- eligibility review
- LTV / churn risk / internal score / scoring threshold
- approved / issued / ordered / shipped / on the way / completed (as final confirmations)
- Salesforce / Data Cloud / Agentforce / CRM

## Confirmation steps
Final confirmation must include one of:
- "confirmed for this demo"
- "No real payment was processed"
- "Demo status only"

Never imply a real transaction, shipment, or case was opened.
